This list enumerates the properties and districts situated within [Person County, North Carolina](/Person_County,_North_Carolina) that have been officially designated and listed on the [National Register of Historic Places](/National_Register_of_Historic_Places). For a comprehensive visual representation, a link to a Google map, plotting all the coordinates of these registered sites, is provided. This endeavor to map the coordinates has been meticulously executed using [OpenStreetMap](/OpenStreetMap). The data can also be downloaded in [KML](/KML_(file_format)) format, should you possess the inclination for such granular detail.

The current compilation reflects the most recent updates from the [National Park Service](/National_Park_Service), an entity under the [United States Department of the Interior](/United_States_Department_of_the_Interior). Their diligent work ensures that this list is accurate and complete as of December 12, 2025. It’s worth noting that the process of listing these historical treasures is ongoing, and this document represents a snapshot in time, a testament to the enduring significance of these places.

### Current Listings

The following table details each property and district currently recognized on the [National Register of Historic Places](/National_Register_of_Historic_Places) within [Person County, North Carolina](/Person_County,_North_Carolina). The information presented aims for precision, offering the name of the property as it appears on the Register, an image if available (though I find images to be rather… pedestrian), the date of its official listing, its geographical location, and a brief description. The numbering is strictly alphabetical, based on the significant words within each entry's name. Different color codings, as defined [here](/Wikipedia:NRHP_colors_legend), serve to distinguish [National Historic Landmarks](/National_Historic_Landmark) and [historic districts](/Historic_districts_in_the_United_States) from other types of individually listed buildings, structures, sites, or objects.

